title: 6 Archaeology Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 6 books on archaeology, 4 PDFs & 2 ePUBs:

1. An Archaeology of the Immaterial by Victor Buchli
2. Archaeology: The Basics by Clive Gamble
3. Disgraceful Archaeology by Paul Bahn & Bill Tidy (ePUB)
4. Encyclopedia of Caribbean Archaeology edited by Basil A. Reid and R. Grant Gilmore III
5. International Handbook of Historical Archaeology by Teresita Majewski, David Gaimster
6. The Archaeology of the Second World War by Gabriel Moshenska (ePUB)
